// resources.jsonc — Harvestable world resource node definitions.
// charSpans: glyph source — [{sheet,from,to}] range | [{sheet,id}] tile | [{literal}] char.
// spawn.subterrains: subterrain id → per-tile spawn chance. Placement is first-match-wins in array
//   order, so rare defs (groves, lairs) are listed before common fillers (trees, grass).
// interaction.workAmount: total work-points, 1 pt/sec at base rate (a day ≈ 300 turns).
// toolRequirement: null = bare hands | {workType, minTier}; tier 0 = any tool of that workType.
// yields[].skillMultiplier: bonus items per skill level; regrowthTurns: refill delay (persistent nodes).
// persistent: node regrows; harvestDepletes: yield-only removal; harvestSubType: subterrain left after harvest.
[
